rComments: Took this class on a whim, and so glad I did! Best professor I've had at this university. Compelling, engaging, encourages students to think critically about material in unique ways. I've never wanted to work so hard for a class. Readings are always interesting. Take a class with Onni!

I don't even know where to begin with Onni. GWS 385 was the best course I've taken at UIUC thus far and it's entirely because Onni is such an outstanding professor. I was inspired every time I came to class and produced some of my best work there. Be mindful, though. If you don't care about social justice, you won't enjoy yourself.

Onni is FABULOUS! They are a great teacher who cares about their students and our ability to learn. They are very creative, engaging, and funning. They taught me to better analyze and critique cultural imperialism, a skill each person should be familiar with. Definitely take a class with this prof if you can. Not too hard but very enjoyable
